The punctuation module
======================

    >>> from pysyte.types.literals import punctuation
    >>> assert 'Handle punctuation' in punctuation.__doc__

Named punctuation
-----------------

The module names the punctuation characters

    >>> assert punctuation.space == ' '
    >>> assert punctuation.question == '?'
    >>> assert punctuation.apostrophe == "'"

And a string with all of them

    >>> assert punctuation.apostrophe in punctuation.punctuation
    >>> assert punctuation.question in punctuation.punctuation
    >>> assert punctuation.colon in punctuation.punctuation
